---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Insurance Policy Changes Guide" description="Understanding how recent insurance policy changes affect Kansas City homeowners">
	<div class="prose max-w-none">
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-6">Insurance Policy Changes Guide</h1>
		<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">Understanding how recent policy changes affect Kansas City homeowners</p>

		<div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-400 p-4 mb-8">
			<div class="flex">
				<div class="flex-shrink-0">
					<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-red-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
					</svg>
				</div>
				<div class="ml-3">
					<h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-red-800">Critical Update</h3>
					<div class="mt-2 text-sm text-red-700">
						<p>Insurance companies are increasingly limiting coverage for roofs 10-15+ years old. This guide explains what you need to know.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
			<div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-800">ACV (Actual Cash Value)</h2>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-red-500 mr-2">•</span>
						<span>Depreciated value based on roof age</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-red-500 mr-2">•</span>
						<span>May not cover full replacement cost</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-red-500 mr-2">•</span>
						<span>Higher out-of-pocket costs for homeowner</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-red-500 mr-2">•</span>
						<span>Common for roofs 10+ years old</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-800">RCV (Replacement Cost Value)</h2>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-green-500 mr-2">•</span>
						<span>Full replacement cost coverage</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-green-500 mr-2">•</span>
						<span>No depreciation applied</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-green-500 mr-2">•</span>
						<span>Lower out-of-pocket costs</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-green-500 mr-2">•</span>
						<span>Typically for newer roofs only</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="bg-blue-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
			<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-800">How Maverick Exteriors Can Help</h3>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
				<ul class="text-sm space-y-2">
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">•</span>
						<span>Professional damage assessment</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">•</span>
						<span>Insurance claim assistance</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">•</span>
						<span>Adjuster meeting support</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
				<ul class="text-sm space-y-2">
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">•</span>
						<span>30+ years of insurance experience</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-blue-600 mr-2">•</span>
						<span>No upfront costs for inspections</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>